name: Warren Lee HILL, petitioner, v. Bruce CHATMAN, Warden.

court.name: Supreme Court of the United States

parties:
Warren Lee HILL, petitioner,
v.

opinions.text: Application for stay of execution of sentence of death presented to Justice THOMAS and by him referred to the Court denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Superior Court of Georgia, Butts County, denied. Justice BREYER and Justice SOTOMAYOR would grant the application for stay of execution.
